# TruthFlow

**TruthFlow** is a decentralized data integrity and real-time outcome resolution protocol on Solana.  
It enables instant verification and settlement for prediction markets, games, and event-driven apps.  

### üß† Key Features
- Decentralized data validation (community-based)
- Real-time event outcome finalization
- Instant bet settlement using Solana programs
- Fully permissionless and open-source

